environment for Python, HTML, CSS, and Markdown.  Here are the needed
apps:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/pythonista-3/id1085978097"&gt;Pythonista 3&lt;/a&gt; -
Python IDE&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/working-copy-git-client/id896694807"&gt;Working Copy&lt;/a&gt; -
A powerful Git client.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/textastic-code-editor-8/id1049254261"&gt;Textastic&lt;/a&gt; -
A multi-purpose text exditor with language support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Note: These are all paid, apps.  But they are worth it if you want to
develop on the go&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="Python, iPad"></category><category term="code"></category><category term="ipad"></category><category term="apple"></category></entry></feed>